refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public Vtiful\Kernel\Validation Vtiful\Kernel\Validation::validationType inttype
Sets the type of data validation, which determines the kind of value that is accepted in the validated cells.

&reftitle.parameters;


  type

   The validation type, one of the Vtiful\Kernel\Validation::TYPE_* constants, such as Vtiful\Kernel\Validation::TYPE_INTEGER, Vtiful\Kernel\Validation::TYPE_DECIMAL or Vtiful\Kernel\Validation::TYPE_LIST.
